Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.26,0:00:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What is wrong, Sir Ken'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.86,0:00:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Hattori-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.06,0:00:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, I played a lot and ended up forgotten to do my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.93,0:00:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"Homework"? Now can you explain, what exactly do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.07,0:00:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure are lucky. You don't have to worry about any homeworks or exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What shall happen if you forgot to do your homework?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.58,0:00:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,My teacher would scold me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.45,0:00:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.45,0:00:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,By just imagining it, my head hurts and I get a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.86,0:00:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't mind being scolded by your parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.43,0:00:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...but you're afraid of your teacher, which means your teacher must be very terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.93,0:00:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.17,0:01:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the time, else you'll be late for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.24,0:01:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a ran-away-boy in your home?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum, did you informed them about Hattori-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.95,0:01:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But because your dad said I must inform the police, just in case, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you have to inform them?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't mind him staying, till we know where he come from.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No, if you inform the police, they'll just take him away!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.13,0:01:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop arguing with your mother. You don't have to scream.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:35.07,Pun,,0,0,0,,{\pos(484,414)}Ninjin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He came from a famous celebrities' village or-so-I-heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:40.14,Pun,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,406)}Ninjin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a famous celebrities' village, but from a Ninja valley, he arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.20,0:01:40.14,TL Note,,0,0,0,,Note: This is a pun on the word \N"Nin" as in "Ninki" which means famous/celebrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.14,0:01:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I have to see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.14,0:01:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's right behind you, Mr. Cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now at front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.85,0:01:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.14,0:01:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Below.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.05,0:01:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.14,0:01:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.14,0:01:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look up! I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.14,0:02:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! Stop fooling around!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.13,0:02:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right above your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Allright, one last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.24,0:02:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I had enough of your mischief.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.08,0:02:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori-{\i1}kun{\i0}, why are you holding a gun? Where did you picked it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It seem to be a nice tool of that cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't possess it, you have to return it to the cop.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.39,0:02:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.43,0:02:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mum, I'll return this gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.30,0:02:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken'ichi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.33,0:02:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.33,0:02:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? You'll be late for the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.33,0:02:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me what you're holding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You musn't bring any dangerous things to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.95,0:02:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks so real!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Throw this dangerous toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It IS a real gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey you! Where'd you picked up that gun from? Tell me the truth-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Cop, you dropped it in my home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you afford to lose your pistol like this? What kind of Cop are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.18,0:03:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't hurry, you'll be late for class.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.12,0:03:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hattori-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't come with me to the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.42,0:03:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,N-nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just talking with myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I said go back to our house!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.63,0:03:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir! If we don't hurry, we both will be late for class!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.31,0:03:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with that shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.91,0:04:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.32,0:04:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:18.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mornin' kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But Sir, you're 30 mins late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.27,0:04:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken'ichi-{\i1}kun{\i0}, how late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.51,0:04:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Yumeko-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.51,0:04:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so late?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.51,0:04:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.51,0:04:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now all of you, show me your homework...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what Hattori-kun is doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ken'ichi-{\i1}kun{\i0}, show me your homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But I forgot to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.93,0:04:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Go and stand outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's being bullied by his teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I'll teach his teacher a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.03,0:05:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's our teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.83,0:05:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please help! Bring me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.83,0:05:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone!...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hattori-{\i1}kun{\i0}, my teacher isn't a bad person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.75,0:05:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot my homework, so I'm the one at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.02,0:05:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're at fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that may be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.23,0:05:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:05:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.97,0:06:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Serves him right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.11,0:06:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You did got what you deserved.